      <h2>About Us</h2><br>
      <p>immiGiving offers an accessible way for individuals from all walks of life to get involved with the immigrant rights movement. We connect immigrant rights leaders to potential volunteers, and in doing so, expand leadership and skill development. Our aim is to build capacity and nurture lasting relationships to empower and strengthen the next generation of leaders.
        Our ultimate goal is to actively engage in and promote the growth of the immigrant rights movement!<br>In 2017, a group of undocumented individuals ventured on a journey collectively to reflect upon the narratives perpetuated in the media around human dignity. We recognize that undocumented individuals are worth more than their labor and productivity. immiGiving is a safe space for immigrant rights leaders and potential volunteers to take back their labor and redefine the immigrant narrative as one of community building and immigrant wellness.  ImmiGiving focuses on the small work that often goes unnoticed and gives them the human capital to turn an event into a movement.</p>
